<h1>Change Email</h1>
<p>Your email address is an extra layer of security for your account and can allow you to regain access to your account if you forgot your password. It also unlocks posting, the most important component in Feed</p>
<input placeholder="Current Password" type="password" id="settingsCurrentPasswordField"/><br>
<input oninput="settingsNewEmailField()" type="email" placeholder="New Email" id="settingsNewEmailField"/><br>
<button class="button" id="settingsNewEmailSubmit" onclick="settingsNewEmailSubmit()" disabled>Submit</button>

<br>

<h1>Email Verification</h1>
<p id="settingsEmailVerifyStatus"></p>
<button class="button hidden" id="settingsSendEmailVerify" onclick="settingsSendEmailVerify()">Send Verification Email</button>
